cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.NE 

The paper is about active learning for natural language processing, which falls under the category of computational linguistics (cs.CL). The paper also extensively uses deep learning models (cs.LG) and Bayesian methods (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper uses acquisition functions commonly used in computer vision (cs.CV) and neural networks (cs.NE).
